nodes.text: Tony Cox (born on March 31, 1958) played Wicket W. Warrick's older brother Widdle Warrick in Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi as well as the television movie spin-offs Caravan of Courage: An Ewok Adventure and Ewoks: The Battle for Endor. Much like co-star Warwick Davis and most of the Ewok performers, Cox is a dwarf actor who has been cast in many roles often of a serious or comedic nature suited to his size.
